OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed for 24 years
OL,7,Ffor a knife attack on a boyfriend and
OL,8,Fgirlfriend in a Middlesbrough bus
OL,9,Fstation.
OL,11,FSamura Mahdi attempted to murder an 18-
OL,12,Fyear-old as he protected his
OL,13,Fgirlfriend as they waited for a bus,
OL,14,Fshortly after 5pm on Monday 20
OL,15,FNovember 2023.
OL,17,FCCTV footage showed Mahdi and Mohammed
OL,18,FGeravandian approach the couple, with
OL,19,FMahdi seen holding a knife at the side
OL,20,Fof his body.
