OL,6,FGeravandian was then seen by the
OL,7,Fvictim placing both hands on his
OL,8,Fwaistband, causing the victim to lunge
OL,9,Fforward and begin a fight with him.
OL,11,FAt the same time, Mahdi pointed the
OL,12,Fknife and stabbed the teenage victim
OL,13,Fwho then fell to the floor.
OL,15,FGeravandian fled the scene and Mahdi
OL,16,Finstead ran at the girl with the
OL,17,Fknife. Her boyfriend intervened and
OL,18,Fwas stabbed numerous times before
OL,19,FMahdi made off through the bus station.
