OL,6,FOfficers and paramedics arrived at the
OL,7,Fscene and the 18-year-old boy was
OL,8,Ftaken to James Cook University
OL,9,FHospital with life-threatening
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FGeravandian was then arrested at his
OL,13,Fhome address on Dawley Close in
OL,14,FThornaby and Mahdi at his property on
OL,15,FNut Lane in Middlesbrough.
OL,17,FBoth were charged with attempted
OL,18,Fmurder and were found guilty in a nine-
OL,19,Fday trial at Teesside Crown Court in
OL,20,FMay.
