OL,6,FMahdi was sentenced to 24 years while
OL,7,FGeravandian was sentenced to 24 years
OL,8,Fwith a further nine months added for
OL,9,Ffailing to provide police with the PIN
OL,10,Fto his phone.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Chris Pringle,
OL,13,Ffrom Cleveland Police's Homicide and
OL,14,FMajor Enquiry Team, said: "This was a
OL,15,Fpremeditated attack to murder a
OL,16,Fteenage boy and his girlfriend.
