OL,6,F"The pair concealed their identity
OL,7,Fbefore brazenly walking into a busy
OL,8,Fbus station to commit violence in
OL,9,Ffront of numerous members of the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,F"To try and protect himself as well as
OL,13,Fhis girlfriend, the victim fought the
OL,14,Fattackers, however he was struck
OL,15,Fnumerous times. His bravery in that
OL,16,Fmoment meant they were both lucky to
OL,17,Fhave survived but will live with the
OL,18,Ftrauma of what took place that day for
OL,19,Fa long time.
