OL,6,F"We also have a teenager and a young
OL,7,Fperson going to prison for a long time
OL,8,Fand that should serve as a stark
OL,9,Freminder that no good can come from
OL,10,Fcarrying a knife. Not only is it
OL,11,Fillegal and you could be jailed if
OL,12,Ffound in possession of one ` but it
OL,13,Fcan have tragic consequences that
OL,14,Fcould cause serious harm including the
OL,15,Floss of life."
